---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Elevon Controls and our engineering focus."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="About Us"
    title="Automation Engineering with a Practical Delivery Focus"
    description="Elevon Controls supports industrial automation projects with a focus on PLC programming, control panel design, HMI/SCADA development, and commissioning support."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p>
        We work primarily with panel builders, system integrators, and contractors, providing
        reliable engineering support that helps teams deliver projects efficiently without
        increasing internal workload.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Approach</p>
      <h2>Clear communication, practical engineering, dependable support</h2>
      <p>
        Our approach is straightforward: clear communication, practical engineering solutions, and
        dependable project support.
      </p>
      <p>
        We focus on delivering work that integrates smoothly into existing projects, avoiding
        unnecessary complexity and delays.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Experience &amp; Focus</p>
      <h2>Strong experience in pump and water-related applications</h2>
      <p>
        We bring strong experience in pump systems and water-related applications, including pump
        stations, pressure boosting systems, wastewater systems, and control and protection logic.
      </p>
      <p>
        This domain knowledge allows us to deliver solutions that are not only functional, but also
        aligned with real operational requirements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">How We Work</p>
      <h2>External automation engineering support across the project lifecycle</h2>
      <p>
        We typically support clients as an external automation engineering partner, providing PLC
        programming, system design, HMI development, and commissioning support.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether working remotely or alongside your team, our goal is to provide consistent,
        reliable engineering input throughout the project lifecycle.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta-band">
    <div class="container prose-block">
      <p class="eyebrow">Partnership</p>
      <h2>Focused on delivery, clarity, and long-term collaboration</h2>
      <p>
        We aim to be a dependable engineering partner for UK automation projects, focused on
        delivery, clarity, and long-term collaboration.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
